  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Veritex, a multiplayer survival game. The goal is to survive versus the wilderness around you, build bases, and fend off other players tat can murder you and take your loot. <br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br>Crafting system<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695360/extras/17f68ee81242cf6fef1492c4df34ba78.poster.avif?t=1549749281\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695360/extras/17f68ee81242cf6fef1492c4df34ba78.webm?t=1549749281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695360/extras/17f68ee81242cf6fef1492c4df34ba78.mp4?t=1549749281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can craft so many items, like torch or a new weapon. Crafting will be your best friend.<br><br>Resource gathering<br><br><br>Beside the crafting system, you need to collect resources. From fruits to wood,s from metal to clothes, our gathering system can provide a full range of resources that will help you to survive in the world of Veritex.<br><br>Single player<br><br>Try the survival experience with the single player mode of Veritex.<br><br>Online multiplayer<br><br>Try to survive among other players in our online mode. Will you be a friend or a foe?",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to Veritex, a multiplayer survival game. The goal is to survive versus the wilderness around you, build bases, and fend off other players tat can murder you and take your loot. <br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br>Crafting system<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695360/extras/17f68ee81242cf6fef1492c4df34ba78.poster.avif?t=1549749281\" width=628 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695360/extras/17f68ee81242cf6fef1492c4df34ba78.webm?t=1549749281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/695360/extras/17f68ee81242cf6fef1492c4df34ba78.mp4?t=1549749281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can craft so many items, like torch or a new weapon. Crafting will be your best friend.<br><br>Resource gathering<br><br><br>Beside the crafting system, you need to collect resources. From fruits to wood,s from metal to clothes, our gathering system can provide a full range of resources that will help you to survive in the world of Veritex.<br><br>Single player<br><br>Try the survival experience with the single player mode of Veritex.<br><br>Online multiplayer<br><br>Try to survive among other players in our online mode. Will you be a friend or a foe?",
